725129f-b.title: Queens: 22nd Street - Bridge Plaza North
725129f-b.text:
22nd Street, north from Bridge Plaza North, in Long Island City's industrial area, showing numerous factories and the lumber yard (left) of the Long Island Lumber Company. Across the lumber yard are industrial plants facing on the north side of 41st Avenue. These latter are shown in view
2, but seen from 21st Street.
P. L. Sperr  View 1: December 29, 1936
NO REPRODUCTIONS  View 2: September 5, 1940
725129f-b.folder: 22nd Street & Bridge Plaza North, Queens, NY
